}
</code></pre> <p>The server listens on <code>0.0.0.0</code> (all interfaces) by default. To restrict to localhost only, pass <code>"127.0.0.1"</code> as the host. The default port is <code>8765</code>; pass a different value to the constructor if needed.</p> <p>One client at a time</p> <p>Chiral is designed for a one-to-one connection between a single server and a single policy client. There is no broadcast or multi-client fanout.</p>

